REDUX :-
Alternative to useContext
To avoid prop drilling, i.e. passing data to nested components..
When to use Redux, if our state is being used in multiple components

UseCase :-

1. When is data is being used in multiple components
2. Fine_grain control in debugging, we can timetravel in Rdeux Dev Tool

